#: src/components/HeatAdaptationPanel.tsx:137
#~ msgid "This qualitative tracker uses connector-provided air temperature and relative humidity, Stull's natural-shade wet-bulb approximation, and split-level power relative to current CP. Effective minutes are weighted evidence, not literal exposure time. Wind and solar radiation are excluded, and the stage thresholds plus 7–28 day decay window are Praxys operational estimates rather than a medical or physiological diagnosis."
#~ msgstr "此定性追踪器使用连接器提供的气温和相对湿度、Stull 自然阴影湿球温度近似，以及相对于当前 CP 的分段功率。加权分钟是证据权重，并非实际暴露时长。模型不包含风速和太阳辐射；阶段阈值与 7–28 天衰减窗口均为 Praxys 的操作性估算，不构成医学或生理诊断。"

